channel.title: Un-Named Pk and Skill
channel.description:
[center][IMG]http://i1318.photobucket.com/albums/t657/chachaichai/Un-Named-Server/Serverimage_zps6d8f07a1.png[/img]
Little about the source, i've been working on and off this source for around one year, it's been a long, and slow haul.
For starters, i'm not here to try and say it's going to become the best or the most succesful. All im trying to do, is make a fun and exciting small community, we're people can spend free time, and enjoy it. But also so people like me, can meet others, and have a good time.
Main thing is, I truly do enjoy, skilling, and PvP. So i based this server around that. They both have bonuses, and are economically the same. If you skill you can be just as rich, as a Pvper.
Photo gallery: Please note: More pictures are on the way
[IMG]http://i1318.photobucket.com/albums/t657/chachaichai/Un-Named-Server/uniquebosses_zps842f646b.png[/img]
[IMG]http://i1318.photobucket.com/albums/t657/chachaichai/Un-Named-Server/home_zpsa5cfecdc.png[/img]
[IMG]http://i1318.photobucket.com/albums/t657/chachaichai/Un-Named-Server/overloads_zps457bfbbc.png[/img]
[IMG]http://i1318.photobucket.com/albums/t657/chachaichai/Un-Named-Server/banksearchfeature_zpscdf78003.png[/img]
Note: Please, dont comment rude or annoying things, thanks. Try it out before you post. New- so there, won't be many, on until we gain people.
[url=http://Website:http://unnamedpk.enjin.com/?welcome]Website:http://unnamedpk.enjin.com/?welcome [/url] [/center]
